      <head>Ludwig Christian Erk</head>
      <div>

        <p>German music teacher, choir director, composer, and editor of folksongs and chorales. </p>

        <p>Schenker used Erk's <title level="m">Johann Sebastian Bachs Choralges√§nge und geistliche Arien</title> (Leipzig:
          Peters), Part I (1850), Part II (1865) in his teaching. </p>

        <p>Henry Davey cites Erk's collections of Bach's chorales in <title level="a">Some Points in Bach's
          Treatment of the Chorale,</title> <title level="m">Proceedings of the Musical Association</title> xxiv (1897/98), pp.
          1-22.</p>
      </div>
